gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 124, Nets 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Nets, 124-101. Nikola Jokic led Denver with 26 points, 15 rebounds, and 10 assists and Peyton Watson added a career-high 18 points, seven rebounds, and five assists. Spencer Dinwiddie led the Nets with 17 points, eight assists, and four rebounds. Denver has now won three games in a row and improved to 17-9 on the year (10-1 at home) as the Nets moved to 13-11.
